es qui scis effugere
quam pisces




LACH    nescio alceu quid celas
        satis intellego te taciturum

Job interview et briefing

EXEMPLA:
remeato audacter, mercedem si eris nactus: nunc abi.
iam reuortar ad te: nam est quod inuisam domum.

DROMO
nihil te tacitius umquam uidi alceu
siquidem nomen tuum uerum
etiam saxa uocem magis reddunt
si scis quomodo percontaberis
nec temulentia rem mutat
scitus es [in evading those questions]
[than these fish were in evading your mouth]
[dis moi seulement la derniere fois que tu as mangé]
[et pourtant j'en ai vu des soldats et des parasites]
[chercher un emploi ici auprès de mon maître]
[je ne sais pas ce que tu veux cacher mais écoute]
[je m'en fiche. ca ne me concerne pas]
[tu as le physique pour le job et tu me sembles un bon gars]
[satis placet. laches will be here soon]

HERCULES
[Peu importe d'où je viens tant que je fais mon travail]
[Je ne vous décevrai pas]
[Ducite me. You'll have a happy man and a fidel employee]

DROMO
Credo.

LACHES
Heus. Dromo.

DROMO
Alceu arrived from abroad here if seeking employment.
and I thought i would bring him here.
Don't ask him questions about his past though
he's silent and slippery like a eel

LACHES
Eel-guy. Well he certainly doesn't look like an eel
Those shoulders. That back.
A shamed athlete loosing the games maybe
Who beat you big guy
Maybe i should employ that one

Silence indeed

HERCULES
I can work hard

LACHES
I bet you can. But these isn't work in the field
or in construction we are talking about. You need
some wit with words too. But since you look so
scary i am willing to put you to the test.






