heus tu | lacer||tos(e) ubi | t(e) oblec||tasti | heri
nam t(e) in | palaes||tr(a) exer|centem || certo | scio
uel ma|ne uel || postid  | uidi||sse ne|minem
hem uide|on chae||ream | suspi||ri(um) om|nium
senum | nimi' mi || blandidi|cu's sed || respon|de mi
palaes|tr(a) heri mi | lectus | fuit nec | doleo | factum

I - Uesania : uesania introduces herself, says she's been following hercules on Juno's order and that she herself pities the guy to have to deal with her for so long
II     - Chaerea Phaedria    : chaerea and phaedria discuss the new loner guy that arrived in town. built like an ox. not wanted to deal with anyone. apparently the new coactor for chaera's father
III     - Hercules : hercules laments on his fate. hesitates between feeling ashamed and just acknowledging Juno's being a bad nouerca
IV - Hercules Demea : Hercules gets job briefing as coactor
V - Hercules Puella : Hercules goes to a farm to collect taxes. meets a puella working a the farm
VI - Puella Chaerea : As soon as Hercules leaves, chaera enters to chat up the girl he is in love with who just pushes him back because she's just a game for him not being a citizen
V - Hercules Uilicus    Seruos : Hercules continues his job and fails collecting anything
VI - Hercules Demea : Hercules gets ridiculed for failing the job despite his big muscles
VII - Hercules : laments and gets drunk
VIII - Hercules Iphiclus : Iphiclus appears as a ghost and tells hercules to change his ways
IX - Demea Chaerea : Demea and Chaerea gets into an argument over rumors he is in love with the puella
X - Chaerea Hercules : Chaerea and Hercules get to know each other
XI - Hercules Uilicus : Hercules decides to try collect taxes again knowing about Chaerea issues too now
XII - Hercules Nutrix : Hercules meets the nutrix who recognizes him and shows him the birth tokens of the puella
XIII - Demea Hercules : more arguments between Demea and Hercules about the job
XIV - Chaerea Demea : more arguments between Demea and Chaerea about the girl
XV - Demea: Demea expressing being really mad at everyone
XV - Chaerea Hercules : hercules finally telling chaerea he is the girl's father
XVI - Nutrix Demea Hercules Demea: the big reveal

